    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve totally babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every single service was done right on time. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for your next big road trip, this is the one. You've gotta come see it in person to really appreciate how clean it is!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
